Interesting, Twitter just blocked my account for a tweet that I didn&#x27;t make. Anybody else seeing this sort of thing?<p>Jacques Mattheij
@jmattheij
@Johnrigsby128 @AUtsogn @KyivIndependent Die on the job...
May 2, 2022, 8:44 PM<p>Please note that while we review your appeal, you won’t be able to access your Twitter account. We’ll take a look and will respond as soon as possible.<p>Bunch of amateurs, I&#x27;ve only ever signed in to Twitter from this <i>one</i> single machine and that tweet certainly isn&#x27;t mine.
